headline: Is lululemon's Earnings Outlook Still Aligned With Its Growth Story?

headline: Ralph Lauren rolls out AI-powered assistant to dole out fashion advice
summary: Ask Ralph can suggest products and offer advice based on prompts like “What should I wear to a concert?” and “How can I style my navy-blue men’s blazer?”
